title: Cifer for Co-Chief Bull
body:
I'm submitting this proposal to nominate Cifer for one of the Co-Chief Bull positions for a term of one year.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/cifer_216

If selected, Cifer will serve as Acting Co-Chief Bull until formal legal agreements are executed, a compensation plan has been put in place, and this position is officially accepted by Cifer.
author: 0xc4eeB8020e539C70Ecbd6464F7dB3Fe61de91986
